title: Issue with Worlds Missions
body:
Im having Issues with the Worlds mission - Watch and Earn II
I have watched worlds games live and vods to try and complete this but it wont seem to.
Yes I have been logged in when watching them.
Help Pls {{sticker:sg-janna}}

replies.body:
Have you tried a different browser and/or incognito/private mode?

Failing that, submit a ticket to player support: https://support.riotgames.com/hc/en-us/requests/new
